![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/f10f181d-06e2-4293-9130-7785330a27e6/23092.jpg)

*   ## **_The Last Time is Now Tournament: Rusev def. Damian Priest_**
    

Rusev sticks his fingers in the burned eye injury Aleister Black caused and then hits a Matchka Kick for the win

* * *

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/4521c497-746b-40f0-87f1-8091b9bde941/23095.jpg)

Adam Pearce wants to know if AJ Styles and Dragon Lee have a name. Dragon Lee offers The Dragons with Style, AJ says they'll work on it

* * *

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/0fdd1a53-6e3d-4be0-bf7a-3cb7cd1842a2/23093.jpg)

Maxxine Dupri tells Adam Pearce that she's not ready but ready isn't a feeling, ready is a choice. Maxxine wants Becky.

Maxxine vs Becky for the Intercontinental Championship is on for next week in MSG.

As soon as Adam Pearce walks away, Becky attacks Maxxine.

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/fc50a3ce-aecc-4fc0-a47c-cfeab9a923f9/23094.jpg)

